_sText:
During the build up of a concert, terrorists attacked Dualism and captured 2 hostages, 
offcourse it's the counter-terrorists there duty to take over the place and free the hostages,

the map is a fast action map with different types of routes, close combat, sniper etc
and is mosty indoors

You will get a good idea of the gameplay when you play it with atleast 6 players (3vs3) the more the better with 16vs16 max

contact v33n@hotmail.com
